manufacturer end items to the new BOMs, WIs, and TDP artifacts for all hardware (HW). The end items are
integrated into the forward flow production Test Equipment (TE) and automation at all levels, from piece part
to All Up Round (AUR). TTP will take beta TE scripts and software developed during E&MD and makes them



