FY 2025 Plans:
Complete static fire demonstrations. Complete rocket motor prototyping OTAs, down select prototyping solution,
award rocket motor development, conduct an In Process Review (IPR) to establish the preliminary design and
begin Developmental Test and Verification static fire testing. and integrate inert operational rocket motors in
missile ground test assets. Initiate purchase of Guidance Sections that contain upgraded electronics units that
will be used for testing and in preparation for transition to production activities. Continuing efforts to address
technical challenges with the upgraded electronics units guidance section.
FY 2026 Base Plans:
Complete Developmental Test and Verification static fire testing, conduct an In Process Review (IPR) to
establish the initial product design and begin qualification and insensitive munitions testing. Continue safety
qualification and insensitive munitions testing at the rocket motor level. Build and integrate inert and live rocket
motors in missile ground test assets and All Up Round qualification test assets.
