A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
Key Enablers and Sonobuoy Enhancements (KESE) provides increased P-8A operational flexibility and effectiveness throughout the kill chain. Funding addresses key
enablers such as, uplink/downlink sonobuoy communications assurance, acoustic communications (ACOMMS) on Increment 3 Block 1 (I3B1) aircraft via FR-115 and
P8A Increment 3 Block 2 (I3B2) aircraft and sonobuoy enhancements that include: link availability and assurance, cyber protection and the integration into the AOFP
software.

